      <procstep>
        <procdesc>Dataset copied from the CD obtained from Washington, DC 2005

Child care sites were identified from a database the D.C. Department of Health provided.  A point shapefile was created by geocoding the addresses to the DC Master Address Repository (MAR).  Addresses that did not initially geocode to the MAR were researched, validated, and verified, then added to the MAR and located in the child care layer.</procdesc>
